{"tid":1360393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"For想行山嘅朋友","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:03:46.000Z","uid":8131,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2403753102591590fdb4f5454080d7208391ac3f","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"想行山又想買平裝備嘅巴打絲打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6UOKnj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6UOKnj.png&h=67037ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行山就梗係要必備行山棍 實測非常之硬 個頭非常之尖抓地功能幾好 建議較短d實淨d<br />\n要硬d就貴多少少 價錢74-199都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9u3yg9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9u3yg9.png&h=d73bb14e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行山點解要頭盔 行過山嘅都知要成日烏低身避開d樹枝 撞到個頭就唔好啦 價錢99-169<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiTDnbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiTDnbd.png&h=a8c8e889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包住個頭做咩 夏天太陽熱辣辣 曬傷塊面就唔好啦 <br />\n價錢$129<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqOsfxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqOsfxq.png&h=938f4d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n功能同上 想平d就買呢個啦 價錢$19<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xS8Kq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xS8Kq8.png&h=6de41637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口罩？呢隻後過濾式口罩 香港空氣咁差 唔好以為上到山就好好多 帶咗包你行高多幾米 氣都唔多喘 價錢$74<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3mxrFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3mxrFn.png&h=f458b2ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n護臂 包實隻手臂 防止曬傷 建議呢隻會厚身實淨d 可以用好多次 價錢$45<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rMadma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rMadma.png&h=92a54df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n功用都係包住手臂防止曬傷 呢隻就薄d涼d 價錢$39<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DK8DneV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDK8DneV.png&h=1455cada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n護pad 用途係好似警察訓練警犬一樣 包住個前臂防止被咬 你知行山有幾多流浪狗啦 實測非常之硬 可以放係前臂用護臂包住 咩size都有 價錢$49 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3R5MHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3R5MHT.png&h=374cf287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19JjQ9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19JjQ9A.png&h=c74a3662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行山鞋啊手套果d唔講啦 出面買仲平<br />\n行山最緊要係安全 一定要full gear <br />\n<br />\n利申：迪卡儂打手"},{"pid":"a108d50486ef62e8cfd83b99da8f06612c789bc8","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"最尾果兩張相點del 我唸住send俾個鐘意浮潛嘅朋友咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3485f41ccfa04568d76a64b390af6d20966d86","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"歡迎其他更適合行山嘅gear"},{"pid":"fca0c4912d304965e58c2dc18fca681e7d93b8f5","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d58420cf6a7598449dd7a83495728ba73e344a36","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6b844398d4f97fcb7da34c761241856f69d199c","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0c290ca3fa8e190117cf8d2a4f19f87c5e158dc","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51c8c71613c3bcdcab929564be26624755dd81f2","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f839e9981dea25b98fc2adbe565f1f7e348596d","tid":1360393,"uid":279135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a108d50486ef62e8cfd83b99da8f06612c789bc8","tid":1360393,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime